snippet.textDisplay: Although I haven’t heard all the songs from Pakistan’s Coke Studio, but for a country labelled as intolerant and tunnel-visioned, I found none of their song lyrics as preachy, androcentric and deliberately backward as the ones sung by Maan and Dosanjh.
